# Don't ship dev artifacts into the build context.
# This dramatically speeds up `docker build` since the entire workspace
# would otherwise be tar'd and shipped to the daemon.

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.cache
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store

.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
.cursor

# Local env files — never bake secrets into images
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# But keep example env files
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.*.example

# Misc
README.md
*.md
docker-compose*.yml
